1. Raw Material Handling (Module Definition)

You’ve defined it well; here’s a slightly tightened systems-style version:

Purpose:
Prepare and stabilize incoming raw materials before grinding into raw meal.

Inputs:

Limestone
Clay
Sand
Additives

Outputs:

Homogenized / blended raw material stream

Key Control Variables:

Feed rate (tons/hour) → throughput control
Moisture (%) → affects grinding efficiency and energy use
Particle size distribution → affects downstream mill load and consistency